            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1026.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> eggs</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat (salt prevents the eggs from cracking)</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, boil for exactly&nbsp;8 min for perfect, mid-boiled eggs</p>\r\n<p>Once done, cool the<strong> eggs</strong> by running them under <strong>cold water</strong> for 3 min</p>\r\n<p>Tip: cooling the eggs completely makes them easier to peel</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
