    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the&nbsp;<strong>green beans</strong>&nbsp;in half</p>\r\n<p>Rip the&nbsp;<strong>red gem lettuce</strong>&nbsp;into rough bite-size pieces</p>",
