      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> potatoes</strong> are nearly fork tender, add the <strong>chopped green beans</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 3-4 min or until tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once done, drain and return to the pot</p>\r\n<p>Add a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> with&nbsp;a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> to the<strong> potatoes</strong> and <strong>beans</strong>&nbsp;and mix to combine</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
