    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>dijon mustard</strong> with 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> in a small bowl</p>\r\n<p>Peel the <strong>garlic</strong> and grate it into the bowl (not a fan of raw garlic? Go easy!) - this is your <strong>french dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
